data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! JUST DROPPED PRICE   MAKE AN OFFER!  Large Corner Move-In Ready home in Lower Moyamensing in the heart of South Philadelphia. This beautiful home has been freshly painted and boasts 3 nice-sized Bedrooms, and 2.5 Baths and has plenty of space on the above-ground floors. The fully finished basement is plush with a Full Bath with a large tub and a Laundry room that has extra storage space. What an ideal extra space for entertaining, and relaxing! The Gray Shaker kitchen cabinets line the kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops with a breakfast bar and room for a dining table. The living room is showered with recessed lighting and is wide and has plenty of room for entertaining, with a powder room for guests. Upstairs are  3 large bedrooms and a recently renovated modern bathroom with a double vanity and sliding glass shower door. This corner home gets showered with natural light from 3 sides. With a "WalkScore" of 94, 2554 S Sartain Street is within walking distance to all of your daily errands and just a couple blocks from the Broad Street Line.
